  <brief_title>Sofosbuvir/Velpatasvir in Adults With Chronic Hepatitis C Virus Infection Who Are on Dialysis for End Stage Renal Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>SOF/VEL ESRD</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Multicenter, Open-Label Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Sofosbuvir/Velpatasvir for 12 Weeks in Subjects With Chronic HCV Infection Who Are on Dialysis for End Stage Renal Disease</official_title>
